---
// English AegisTalk page (condensed) — full EN coverage lands in Phase 3
import Base from '../../../layouts/Base.astro';
---
<Base
  title="AegisTalk — AI scam interception inside encrypted calls & chats"
  description="AegisTalk: end-to-end encrypted messenger with a three-layer on-device AI scam engine and free Family Guard. Distributed exclusively via official app stores."
  lang="en"
  altPath="/aegistalk"
  active="aegistalk"
>
  <section class="hero" style="min-height:75vh">
    <div class="hero-content">
      <div class="hero-badge">💬 AegisTalk</div>
      <h1>The first messenger that intercepts scams<br /><span class="gradient">inside encrypted calls</span></h1>
      <p>
        Messages, calls and files — end-to-end encrypted. And an AI guard standing inside the
        conversation: the moment a scam script appears, a red-shield alert fires. All analysis
        runs on your device; your privacy stays intact.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="ai-engine">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="section-label">// PROTECTION</div>
      <h2 class="section-title reveal">Three layers, one engine</h2>
      <div class="ai-layers">
        <div class="ai-layer reveal">
          <div class="layer-badge l1">L1</div>
          <div class="layer-info"><h4>Blocklists — instant interception</h4><p>Malicious domains, typosquatting, scam keywords — known threats blocked in under a millisecond.</p></div>
        </div>
        <div class="ai-layer reveal">
          <div class="layer-badge l2">L2</div>
          <div class="layer-info"><h4>Expert rules × semantic ML fusion</h4><p>53,640 explainable rules fused with a &lt;6MB fastText model. 98.5% detection, F1 0.981 on 26,137 real-world messages (in-domain evaluation).</p></div>
        </div>
        <div class="ai-layer reveal">
          <div class="layer-badge l3">L3</div>
          <div class="layer-info"><h4>Behavioral baseline — anomaly detection</h4><p>26 conversational features train a personal baseline locally. "Three weeks of chatting, then suddenly asking for money" — the behavior layer sees it.</p></div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="cta-section" id="download">
    <h2>Get AegisTalk</h2>
    <p>Coming to the App Store and Google Play.</p>
    <div class="hero-actions" style="justify-content:center">
      <span class="btn-ghost" style="cursor:default">🍎 App Store · coming soon</span>
      <span class="btn-ghost" style="cursor:default">🤖 Google Play · coming soon</span>
    </div>
    <p style="margin-top:2rem;color:var(--warn);font-weight:700">
      ⚠️ AegisTalk is distributed exclusively through official app stores — any "web version" is a scam.
    </p>
  </section>
</Base>
